# Ludo
## Multiplayer Ludo Game Made in Unity
This is a multi-player game. However, due to a lack of budget, it is not possible to make it an online multi-player game. Therefore, users have to play it on a single device.

## Features
* Optimized only for Android devices
* 2, 3, or 4 players can play at a time
* All the rules of the traditional Ludo game are maintained during development
* Start screen, winning screen, and exit screen are included
* Cheerful background music
* Simple, user-friendly UI
* Fact: Over 4000+ lines of code were written in C# to make this whole app run

